with pname
\fBGL_SYNC_STATUS\fR
ignores the other parameters and returns
\fBGL_SIGNALED\fR
in
\fIvalues\fR\&.
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
\fBglGetQueryObjectuiv\fR
with pname
